title: Mary Lou Williams - (1945-47) & (1949-51) Classics
description:
MARY LOU WILLIAMS - TWO CHRONOLOGICAL CLASSICS KNOCK-OFF CDS

I believe knock-off is the correct term for these two CDs. They were obviously not manufactured by MELODIE. Someone copied the original CDs, scanned the artwork and manufactured these. I can't say whether the sound is as good as, or the same as the original CDs because I do not have them. They sound OK enough to me. I put them through the TAU analyzer for whatever that is worth and the verdict was CDDA for both.
